      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "INDY MELMEN (6) box seated early before forging to the lead turning and lifting to score (29.40) at Sandown in a Mix 6/7 over 515m. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Looks to have an edge on most of these. MAXI GRIN (8) goes very well at the distance with two wins and a placing from five starts. Below best last time at this track (30.56) in a Grade 5 H, finishing a 9 length fifth. Can feature in the finish. LUSH HOUR (4) has a strong record this trip including four wins from seven starts. Comes off a (29.79) win last time, scoring by 1.3 lengths in a Grade 5 over 515m at Sandown. Among the main chances. LADY RAPID (2) was a last-start winner at big odds and is in the mix again.",
